# apps/backend/src/

## Responsibility
Application composition layer: wires startup, global plugins, route groups, shared libs, workers, and compatibility endpoints.

## Design
Modular Elysia composition. src/index.ts is the main composition root; modules export feature routers from src/modules/index.ts; shared infrastructure lives in src/lib and src/plugins.

## Flow
Startup loads env, selects APP_MODE, mounts CORS + auth/openapi/context/socket plugins, then groups feature routers under /api. Route handlers delegate to module services, which call Prisma/Redis/external SDKs.

## Integration
Connects feature routers to shared context and infrastructure, and exposes compatibility endpoints for older clients alongside the newer module-based API surface.

